{"tid":1874481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【青衣又中】懷疑新增一宗武漢肺炎確診個案","createTime":"2020-02-11T08:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T08:36:07.000Z","uid":177811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8e6dd8a244d9168a68f01dd14d963fdbb10b9b47","tid":1874481,"uid":177811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:33:07.000Z","msg":"⚠⚠⚠緊急通知⚠⚠⚠<br />\n<br />\n達仔收到有關消息，指翠怡花園有一宗新冠狀病毒懷疑確診個案，暫時得知消息該名人士為翠怡花園2座住戶。我正在向衛生署防護中心了解進一步情況，同時要求管理處立即啟動緊急應變措施。<br />\n<br />\n截至下午4時15分，已得知的訊息如下：<br />\n- 該名病人曾於2月3日、5日及7日到灝景灣「聯合醫務中心」求診<br />\n- 該名病人為康美樓女確診者的密切接觸者<br />\n<br />\n我知道大家一定會好緊張同驚，有最新消息，我會第一時間為大家通知，請大家注意個人衛生。<br />\n<br />\n達仔今晚10點鐘會聯同幾個青衣區議員一同開Facebook Live 與大家詳細交代情況。<br />\n<br />\n🚨勤倒清水/稀釋漂白水落廁所渠口 <br />\n🚨保持渠口濕潤 <br />\n🚨出入必須戴口罩<br />\n🚨勤洗手🚨勿捽眼<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n#涌美老屋村 #海欣花園 #翠怡花園 #藍田村 #新屋村 #海悅花園 #大王下村 #青輝新村 #青裕新村 #鹽田角村 #楓樹窩村 #信義新村 #黃俊達 #達仔<br />\n<br />\n☎️ 達仔電話：9222-2372<br />\n💻 <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/mity.chuntat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmity.chuntat&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=d40d81e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/mity.chuntat</a><br />\n📨 tsingyi.chuntat@gmail.com<br />\n📮 定期接收區議會工作匯報：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Fg91Qs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Fg91Qs&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=583e8445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Fg91Qs</a>"},{"pid":"f69fc6a2c9d71638f5acd5af4c8e57349049fbc4","tid":1874481,"uid":177811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:33:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=207881103941376&amp;id=100833411312813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D207881103941376%26id%3D100833411312813&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=a72d71ef\" data-auto-link target